        Start
                    │
                    ▼
        Read candlesCount (number of candles)
                    │
                    ▼
        Read the list of candles
                    │
                    ▼
        Find the maximum height in the candles list
                    │
                    ▼
        Count how many candles have the maximum height
                    │
